        <seg type="rubrication">The names <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢየሲስ፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሣህለ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign>,
        titles of the homilies, elements of numerals and punctuation signs.</seg>
        <date notBefore="1800" notAfter="1812" resp="PRS10171Wright"/>
    </handNote>

</handDesc>

    <additions>
        <list>
